SELECT
cpst1.recid as RECID
,cpst1.defaultdimension as DEFAULTDIMENSION
,cpst1.transactioncode as TRANSACTIONCODE
,cpst1.inventdimid as INVENTDIMID
,cpst1.itemid as ITEMID
,cpst1.deliverypostaladdress as DELIVERYPOSTALADDRESS
,cpst1.salesgroup as SALESGROUP
,cpst1.salesunit as SALESUNIT
,cpst1.deliverydate as DELIVERYDATE
,cpst1.saleslineshippingdateconfirmed as SALESLINESHIPPINGDATECONFIRMED
,cpst1.saleslineshippingdaterequested as SALESLINESHIPPINGDATEREQUESTED
,cpst1.inventtransid as INVENTTRANSID
,cpst1.dataareaid as DATAAREAID
,cpst1.linenum as LINENUM
,cpst1.origsalesid as ORIGSALESID
,cpst1.packingslipid as PACKINGSLIPID
,cpst1.salesid as SALESID
,cpst1.deliverytype as DELIVERYTYPE
,cpst1.inventqty as INVENTQTY
,cpst1.qty as QTY
,cpst1.priceunit as PRICEUNIT
,cpst1.valuemst as VALUEMST
,cpst1.modifieddatetime as MODIFIEDDATETIME
,def1.BUSINESS_UNIT as DEFAULTDIMENSION_BUSINESS_UNIT
,def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,st1.smmcampaignid as SALESTABLE_SMMCAMPAIGNID
,st1.markupgroup as SALESTABLE_MARKUPGROUP
,st1.linedisc as SALESTABLE_LINEDISC
,st1.salespoolid as SALESTABLE_SALESPOOLID
,st1.pricegroupid as SALESTABLE_PRICEGROUPID
,st1.workersalesresponsible as SALESTABLE_WORKERSALESRESPONSIBLE
,st1.documentstatus as SALESTABLE_DOCUMENTSTATUS
,st1.returnstatus as SALESTABLE_RETURNSTATUS
,'2' as SALESTABLE_SALESSTATUS
,st1.salestype as SALESTABLE_SALESTYPE
,st1.atagent as SALESTABLE_ATAGENT
,st1.shipcarrierblindshipment as SALESTABLE_SHIPCARRIERBLINDSHIPMENT
,st1.shipcarrierexpeditedshipment as SALESTABLE_SHIPCARRIEREXPEDITEDSHIPMENT
,st1.orderblocked as SALESTABLE_ORDERBLOCKED
,st1.mcrorderstopped as SALESTABLE_MCRORDERSTOPPED
,st1.shipcarrierfuelsurcharge as SALESTABLE_SHIPCARRIERFUELSURCHARGE
,st1.modifieddatetime as SALESTABLE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,cpsj1.invoiceaccount as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVOICEACCOUNT
,cpsj1.orderaccount as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_ORDERACCOUNT
,cpsj1.dlvmode as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DLVMODE
,cpsj1.dlvterm as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DLVTERM
,cpsj1.invoicepostaladdress as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVOICEPOSTALADDRESS
,cpsj1.shipcarrierid as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_SHIPCARRIERID
,cpsj1.inventlocationid as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVENTLOCATIONID
,cpsj1.workersalestaker as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_WORKERSALESTAKER
,cpsj1.ntt_deliverystatus as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
,cpsj1.documentdate as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DOCUMENTDATE
,cpsj1.billofladingid as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_BILLOFLADINGID
,cpsj1.internalpackingslipid as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INTERNALPACKINGSLIPID
,cpsj1.ledgervoucher as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_LEDGERVOUCHER
,cpsj1.purchaseorder as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_PURCHASEORDER
,cpsj1.ebcoverridestatus as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_EBCOVERRIDESTATUS
,cpsj1.modifieddatetime as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,id1.configid as INVENTDIM1_CONFIGID
,id1.modifieddatetime as INVENTDIM1_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,idc1.pdmstatus as INVENTDIMCOMBINATION_PDMSTATUS
,idc1.modifieddatetime as INVENTDIMCOMBINATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,scp1.carrierid as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERID
,scp1.shipdate as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_SHIPDATE
,scp1.carriername as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERNAME
,scp2.shipdate as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE2_SHIPDATE
,sl1.linedisc as SALESLINE_LINEDISC
,sl1.linepercent as SALESLINE_LINEPERCENT
,sl1.returnstatus as SALESLINE_RETURNSTATUS
,'2' as SALESLINE_SALESSTATUS
,sl1.shipcarrierdlvtype as SALESLINE_SHIPCARRIERDLVTYPE
,sl1.complete as SALESLINE_COMPLETE
,sl1.orderblocked as SALESLINE_ORDERBLOCKED
,sl1.scrap as SALESLINE_SCRAP
,sl1.stockedproduct as SALESLINE_STOCKEDPRODUCT
,sl1.modifieddatetime as SALESLINE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,mslds1.dropshipment as MCRSALESLINEDROPSHIPMENT_DROPSHIPMENT
,sct1.ntt_deliverydate as SHIPCARRIERTRACKING_NTT_DELIVERYDATE
,sct1.trackingnumber as SHIPCARRIERTRACKING_TRACKINGNUMBER
,tet1.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE1_ENUMVALUELABEL_DOCUMENTSTATUS
,tet2.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE2_ENUMVALUELABEL_RETURNSTATUSHEADER
,tet3.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE3_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESSTATUSHEADER
,tet4.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE4_ENUMVALUELABEL_RETURNSTATUSLINE
,tet5.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE5_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESSTATUSLINE
,tet6.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE6_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESTYPE
,tet7.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE7_ENUMVALUELABEL_SHIPCARRIERDLVTYPE
,tet8.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE8_ENUMVALUELABEL_NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
,tet9.enumvaluelabel as TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE9_ENUMVALUELABEL_TRADELINEDLVTYPE,
ps1.name as PDMSTATUS_NAME
,convert(varchar(max),hashbytes('SHA2_256', concat(isnull(cpst1.recid, 0), 
'~', isnull(scp1.carrierid, ''), '~',
 isnull(scp1.shipdate, '1950-01-01 00:00:00'), '~',
  isnull(scp1.carriername, ''), '~',
   isnull(scp2.shipdate, '1950-01-01 00:00:00'), '~',
    isnull(mslds1.dropshipment, 0), '~',
	 isnull(sct1.ntt_deliverydate, '1950-01-01 00:00:00'), '~', 
	 isnull(sct1.trackingnumber, ''))),2) as HK_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS_EXT_HASH_KEY
,(SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate)
 FROM (VALUES (cpst1.modifieddatetime),
  (isnull(def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(st1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(id1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
  , (isnull(sl1.modifieddatetime, '1950-01-01'))
) AS UpdateDate(LastUpdateDate)) as LATEST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
FROM
dbo.CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS cpst1
left join (select distinct cpst1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
				, max(
					case when da1.NAME = 'BusinessUnit' then davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE
						else null
						end
					) over (partition by cpst1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as BUSINESS_UNIT
				, max(
					(select max(i) from (values (davsi1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (dav1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (da1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (desc1.DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME)) AS T(i))
					) over (partition by cpst1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
			from (select distinct DEFAULTDIMENSION from dbo.CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS) cpst1
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM davsi1 on
				cpst1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE dav1 on
				davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE = dav1.RECID
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE da1 on
				dav1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da1.RECID
			left join (select dft1.VALUE, da2.NAME, dft1.DESCRIPTION
							, (select max(i) from (values (dft1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (dadc1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (da2.MODIFIEDDATETIME)) AS T(i)) as DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME
						from dbo.DIMENSIONFINANCIALTAG dft1
						left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEDIRCATEGORY dadc1 on
							dft1.FINANCIALTAGCATEGORY = dadc1.DIRCATEGORY
						left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE da2 on
							dadc1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da2.RECID) desc1 on
				davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE = desc1.VALUE and
				da1.NAME = desc1.NAME
			) def1 on
	cpst1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
left join dbo.SALESTABLE st1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = st1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.SALESID = st1.SALESID
left join (select DATAAREAID, PACKINGSLIPID, SALESID, DELIVERYDATE
			, INVOICEACCOUNT, ORDERACCOUNT, DLVMODE, DLVTERM, INVOICEPOSTALADDRESS, SHIPCARRIERID, INVENTLOCATIONID, WORKERSALESTAKER, NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS, DOCUMENTDATE, BILLOFLADINGID, INTERNALPACKINGSLIPID, LEDGERVOUCHER, PURCHASEORDER, EBCOVERRIDESTATUS
			, MODIFIEDDATETIME
		from dbo.CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR cpsj10
		inner join (select RECID
					, row_number() over (partition by DATAAREAID, PACKINGSLIPID, SALESID, DELIVERYDATE order by MODIFIEDDATETIME desc) as ROW_NUM
				from dbo.CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR) cpsj11 on
			cpsj11.ROW_NUM = 1 and
			cpsj10.RECID = cpsj11.RECID) cpsj1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = cpsj1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.PACKINGSLIPID = cpsj1.PACKINGSLIPID and
	cpst1.SALESID = cpsj1.SALESID and
	cpst1.DELIVERYDATE = cpsj1.DELIVERYDATE
left join dbo.INVENTDIM id1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = id1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.INVENTDIMID = id1.INVENTDIMID
left join (select idc10.DATAAREAID, idc10.ITEMID, id10.CONFIGID, idc10.PDMSTATUS
			, max(id10.MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MODIFIEDDATETIME
		from dbo.INVENTDIMCOMBINATION idc10
		left join dbo.INVENTDIM id10 on
			idc10.DATAAREAID = id10.DATAAREAID and
			idc10.INVENTDIMID = id10.INVENTDIMID
		group by idc10.DATAAREAID, idc10.ITEMID, id10.CONFIGID, idc10.PDMSTATUS) idc1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = idc1.DATAAREAID and
	id1.CONFIGID = idc1.CONFIGID and
	cpst1.ITEMID = idc1.ITEMID
left join dbo.SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE scp1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = scp1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.PACKINGSLIPID = scp1.PACKINGSLIPID and
	cpst1.ORIGSALESID = scp1.SALESID
left join dbo.SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE scp2 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = scp2.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.PACKINGSLIPID = scp2.PACKINGSLIPID and
	cpst1.SALESID = scp2.SALESID
left join dbo.SALESLINE sl1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = sl1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.INVENTTRANSID = sl1.INVENTTRANSID
left join dbo.MCRSALESLINEDROPSHIPMENT mslds1 on
	sl1.DATAAREAID = mslds1.DATAAREAID and
	sl1.RECID = mslds1.SALESLINE
left join (select DATAAREAID, PACKINGSLIPID, SALESID, NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
			, max(NTT_DELIVERYDATE) as NTT_DELIVERYDATE
			, max(TRACKINGNUMBER) as TRACKINGNUMBER
		from dbo.SHIPCARRIERTRACKING
		group by DATAAREAID, PACKINGSLIPID, SALESID, NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS) sct1 on
	cpst1.DATAAREAID = sct1.DATAAREAID and
	cpst1.PACKINGSLIPID = sct1.PACKINGSLIPID and
	cpst1.ORIGSALESID = sct1.SALESID and
	cpsj1.NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS = sct1.NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'DocumentStatus'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet1 on
	st1.DOCUMENTSTATUS = tet1.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'ReturnStatusHeader'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet2 on
	st1.RETURNSTATUS = tet2.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'SalesStatus'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet3 on
	'2' = tet3.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'ReturnStatusLine'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet4 on
	sl1.RETURNSTATUS = tet4.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'SalesStatus'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet5 on
	 '2' = tet5.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'SalesType'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet6 on
	st1.SALESTYPE = tet6.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'ShipCarrierDlvType'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet7 on
	sl1.SHIPCARRIERDLVTYPE = tet7.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'NTT_DeliveryStatus'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet8 on
	cpsj1.NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS = tet8.ENUMVALUE
left join (select ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE
			, max(ENUMVALUELABEL) as ENUMVALUELABEL
		from dbo.TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE
		where ENUMNAME = 'TradeLineDlvType'
		group by ENUMNAME, ENUMVALUE) tet9 on
	cpst1.DELIVERYTYPE = tet9.ENUMVALUE
	left join dbo.PDMSTATUS ps1 on
	idc1.PDMSTATUS = ps1.RECID

     , cpst1.origsalesid                    as ORIGSALESID

     , cpst1.deliverytype                   as DELIVERYTYPE
     , cpst1.inventqty                      as INVENTQTY
     , cpst1.qty                            as QTY
     , cpst1.priceunit                      as PRICEUNIT
     , cpst1.valuemst                       as VALUEMST
     , cpst1.modifieddatetime               as MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , def1.business_unit                   as DEFAULTDIMENSION_BUSINESS_UNIT
     , def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , st1.smmcampaignid                    as SALESTABLE_SMMCAMPAIGNID
     , st1.markupgroup                      as SALESTABLE_MARKUPGROUP
     , st1.linedisc                         as SALESTABLE_LINEDISC
     , st1.salespoolid                      as SALESTABLE_SALESPOOLID
     , st1.pricegroupid                     as SALESTABLE_PRICEGROUPID
     , st1.workersalesresponsible           as SALESTABLE_WORKERSALESRESPONSIBLE
     , st1.documentstatus                   as SALESTABLE_DOCUMENTSTATUS
     , st1.returnstatus                     as SALESTABLE_RETURNSTATUS
     , st1.salesstatus                      as SALESTABLE_SALESSTATUS

     , st1.shipcarrierexpeditedshipment     as SALESTABLE_SHIPCARRIEREXPEDITEDSHIPMENT
     , st1.orderblocked                     as SALESTABLE_ORDERBLOCKED
     , st1.mcrorderstopped                  as SALESTABLE_MCRORDERSTOPPED
     , st1.shipcarrierfuelsurcharge         as SALESTABLE_SHIPCARRIERFUELSURCHARGE
     , st1.modifieddatetime                 as SALESTABLE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , cpsj1.invoiceaccount                 as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVOICEACCOUNT
     , cpsj1.orderaccount                   as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_ORDERACCOUNT
     , cpsj1.dlvmode                        as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DLVMODE
     , cpsj1.dlvterm                        as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DLVTERM
     , cpsj1.invoicepostaladdress           as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVOICEPOSTALADDRESS
     , cpsj1.shipcarrierid                  as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_SHIPCARRIERID
     , cpsj1.inventlocationid               as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INVENTLOCATIONID
     , cpsj1.workersalestaker               as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_WORKERSALESTAKER
     , cpsj1.ntt_deliverystatus             as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
     , cpsj1.documentdate                   as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_DOCUMENTDATE
     , cpsj1.billofladingid                 as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_BILLOFLADINGID
     , cpsj1.internalpackingslipid          as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_INTERNALPACKINGSLIPID
     , cpsj1.ledgervoucher                  as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_LEDGERVOUCHER
     , cpsj1.purchaseorder                  as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_PURCHASEORDER
     , cpsj1.ebcoverridestatus              as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_EBCOVERRIDESTATUS
     , cpsj1.modifieddatetime               as CUSTPACKINGSLIPJOUR_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , id1.configid                         as INVENTDIM1_CONFIGID
     , id1.modifieddatetime                 as INVENTDIM1_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , idc1.productlifecyclestateid         as INVENTDIMCOMBINATION_PDMSTATUS
     , idc1.modifieddatetime                as INVENTDIMCOMBINATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , scp1.tpxcarriercode                  as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERID
     , scp1.deliverydate                    as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_SHIPDATE
     , scp1.name                            as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERNAME
     , cpsj1.tpxscpshipdate                 as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE2_SHIPDATE
     , sl1.linedisc                         As SALESLINE_LINEDISC
     , sl1.linepercent                      As SALESLINE_LINEPERCENT
     , sl1.returnstatus                     As SALESLINE_RETURNSTATUS
     , sl1.salesstatus                      As SALESLINE_SALESSTATUS
     , sl1.shipcarrierdlvtype               As SALESLINE_SHIPCARRIERDLVTYPE
     , sl1.complete                         As SALESLINE_COMPLETE
     , sl1.orderblocked                     As SALESLINE_ORDERBLOCKED
     , sl1.scrap                            As SALESLINE_SCRAP
     , sl1.stockedproduct                   As SALESLINE_STOCKEDPRODUCT
     , sl1.modifieddatetime                 As SALESLINE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , mslds1.dropshipment                  As MCRSALESLINEDROPSHIPMENT_DROPSHIPMENT
     , sct1.ntt_deliverydate                As SHIPCARRIERTRACKING_NTT_DELIVERYDATE
     , sct1.trackingnumber                  As SHIPCARRIERTRACKING_TRACKINGNUMBER
     , tet1.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE1_ENUMVALUELABEL_DOCUMENTSTATUS
     , tet2.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE2_ENUMVALUELABEL_RETURNSTATUSHEADER
     , tet3.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE3_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESSTATUSHEADER
     , tet4.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE4_ENUMVALUELABEL_RETURNSTATUSLINE
     , tet5.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE5_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESSTATUSLINE
     , tet6.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE6_ENUMVALUELABEL_SALESTYPE
     , tet7.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE7_ENUMVALUELABEL_SHIPCARRIERDLVTYPE
     , tet8.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE8_ENUMVALUELABEL_NTT_DELIVERYSTATUS
     , tet9.enumvaluelabel                  As TIMEXTENDERENUMTABLE9_ENUMVALUELABEL_TRADELINEDLVTYPE
     , scp1.tpxcarriercode                  as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERID
     , scp1.deliverydate                    as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_SHIPDATE
     , scp1.name                            as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE1_ORIG_CARRIERNAME
     , cpsj1.tpxscpshipdate                 as SHIPCARRIERPACKAGE2_SHIPDATE
     , convert(   varchar (Max)
                , hashbytes(   'sha2_256'
                             , concat(   isnull(   cpst1.recid
                                                 , 0
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   scp1.tpxcarriercode
                                                 , ''
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   scp1.deliverydate
                                                 , '1950-01-01 00:00:00'
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   scp1.name
                                                 , ''
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   cpsj1.tpxscpshipdate
                                                 , '1950-01-01 00:00:00'
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   mslds1.dropshipment
                                                 , 0
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   sct1.ntt_deliverydate
                                                 , '1950-01-01 00:00:00'
                                               )
                                       , '~'
                                       , isnull(   sct1.trackingnumber
                                                 , ''
                                               )
                                       , getdate()
                                     )
                           )
                , 2
              )                             As HK_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS_EXT_HASH_KEY
     , (
           Select max(lastupdatedate)
            From
            (
                Values --(cpst1.modifieddatetime),
                    (
                        isnull(   def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   st1.modifieddatetime
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   id1.modifieddatetime
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   sl1.modifieddatetime
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
            ) As updatedate ( lastupdatedate )
       )                                    As LATEST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
 From
    dataverse_nalatst_cds2_workspace_unqe092999b0ee2ee1190466045bda8c.dbo.custpackingsliptrans                     cpst1
     Left Join
     (
         Select distinct
                cpst1.defaultdimension
              , max(   case
                           when da1.name = 'businessunit'
                               then davsi1.displayvalue
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by cpst1.defaultdimension ) as business_unit
              , max((
                        select max(i)
                         from
                         (
                             values
                                 (
                                     davsi1.modifieddatetime
                                 )
                               , (
                                     dav1.modifieddatetime
                                 )
                               , (
                                     da1.modifieddatetime
                                 )
                               , (
                                     desc1.desc_modifieddatetime
                                 )
                         ) as t ( i )
                    )
